DTSTART:20260308
DTEND:20260309
SUMMARY:Part Closure: MILDMAY LINE: Sunday 8 March\, no service between 
 Camden Road and Stratford. Replacement bus service S operates between 
 Camden Road and Stratford via Holloway Road (for Piccadilly line)\, 
 Highbury & Islington\, Canonbury (St Paul's Road)\, Dalston Junction (for 
 Dalston Kingsland)\, Hackney Central\, Homerton and Hackney Wick. In 
 addition\, the 0848 Willesden Junction to Clapham Junction and 0915 Gospel
  Oak to Clapham Junction trains start at Shepherds Bush\, the 0951 Camden 
 Road to Richmond train will not run\, and the 0956 Camden Road to Clapham 
 Junction train starts at Willesden Junction.
END:VEVENT
