SUMMARY:Part Closure: ELIZABETH LINE: Sunday 8 March\, no service between 
 Stratford and Shenfield. The limited ELIZABETH LINE services to/from 
 Liverpool Street will also not operate. There will also be no GREATER 
 ANGLIA services between Liverpool Street and Southend Victoria / 
 Southminster. Replacement buses operate.
