SUMMARY:Part Closure: DOCKLANDS LIGHT RAILWAY: Saturday 7 and Sunday 8 
 March\, no service between Poplar / Stratford International and Beckton / 
 Woolwich Arsenal. Use JUBILEE LINE services between Stratford and Canning 
 Town\, and ELIZABETH LINE connections between Canary Wharf\, Custom House 
 and Woolwich (for Woolwich Arsenal). Replacement buses operate.
